<h1>About BeaverTracks</h1>

<% cache :action => 'about', :part =>'content' do %>
<div id ="about">
  <p>BeaverTracks is an interactive mobile guide and walking tour of Oregon State University's historical locations.</p> 
  <p>At each of the 22 locations, you get a brief history  and can browse a catalog of historic images. Depending on your mobile device you can also take a walking tour of the historic sites.</p>
</div>

