<p><a name="credit"><%= image_tag 'expert.png' %></a>
All images in BeaverTracks are from the OSU <a href="http://scarc.library.oregonstate.edu">Special Collections &amp; Archives Research Center (SCARC)</a> collections and permission must be obtained to publish or permanently display reproductions of the materials. Please contact <a href="mailto:scarc@oregonstate.edu">OSU SCARC</a> with requests or questions. All images in BeaverTracks can also be found on <a href ="http://www.flickr.com/photos/osuarchives/">OSU SCARC Flickr photostream</a>.</p>
<p>BeaverTracks was developed by OSU Libraries staff. It was inspired by NCSU Libraries' project WolfWalk. The virtual walking tour is based on the print publication <em>OSU Buildings &amp; Services Walking Tour</em>.</p>
